SimpleFormChecker is a plugin for jquery that make the validation of forms easier.
See full description at: http://alexju.be/archive/sfc/

SimpleFormChecker is well documented script so you don't need much information to make it work.    
I will explain some settings and options here:


+-|PARAMETERS|---------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|                      |            |                                                       |
|  Parameter           |  Default   |  Description                                          |
|                      |            |                                                       |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  asterix             |  "string"  |  Asterix is shown near a field that is required       |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  errorMessage        |  "string"  |  Error-message-element                                |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  requiredClass       |  "string"  |  Class for required fields                            |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  checkOnChange       |  true      |  Validate field if it's changed                       |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  updateOnType        |  true      |  Update some fields on key up                         |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  scrollToErrorField  |  true      |  Scroll to the first error field                      |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  animationTime       |  250       |  Animation time                                       |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  scrollTime          |  500       |  Animation time while scrolling to top                |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  emptyErrorText      |  "string"  |  Error text that is shown for a required field        |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  formErrorText       |  "string"  |  This text will be shown if a form is invalid         |
|                      |            |  (use with data-errmessage="xxx" on the form)         |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+
|  errorText.OBJECT    |  "string"  |  Error messages for Regex-validators                  |
|                      |            |  Now also for custom checks                           |
+----------------------+------------+-------------------------------------------------------+


You can find all the information on various validators in the source, just check them there ;)


